 relatively hot ($T\\gtrsim800\\,$K),\nand consequently massive ($M_{\\text{disk}}\\sim0.5\\,M_J$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Feb 2014 21:07:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
