ver, but Centaurs\nwith characteristics predicted by the model (e.g., large semimajor axes, above\n60 au, or high inclinations, above 40 degrees) are increasingly being found by\nobservers. The model predicts that the mean physical lifetime of all comets in\nthe region q<1.5 AU is less than approximately 200 revolutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2014 12:46:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-07"}
